my:Nick_Bostrom a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Nick Bostrom" ;
my:comment "A philosopher and director of the Future of Humanity Institute, Bostrom has written extensively on the risks and challenges of advanced AI." .

my:Stuart_Russell a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Stuart Russell" ;
my:comment "A computer scientist and AI researcher, Russell has made important contributions to the development of AI and has written about the need for value alignment in AI systems." .

my:David_Chalmers a my:Influencer ;
my:label "David Chalmers" ;
my:comment "A philosopher and cognitive scientist, Chalmers has written extensively on the nature of consciousness and the mind-body problem." .

my:Sean_Carroll a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Sean Carroll" ;
my:comment "A physicist and cosmologist, Carroll has written about the origins of the universe and the nature of reality, and has also explored the implications of AI and quantum computing." .

my:Jürgen_Schmidhuber a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Jürgen Schmidhuber" ;
my:comment "A computer scientist and AI researcher, Schmidhuber has made important contributions to the development of deep learning and has written about the potential risks and benefits of advanced AI." .

my:Robin_Hanson a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Robin Hanson" ;
my:comment "An economist and AI researcher, Hanson has written about the potential economic and social implications of advanced AI." .

my:Vernor_Vinge a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Vernor Vinge" ;
my:comment "A science fiction author and computer scientist, Vinge has written about the potential risks and benefits of advanced AI in his fiction and non-fiction works." .

my:Peter_Norvig a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Peter Norvig" ;
my:comment "A computer scientist and AI researcher, Norvig has made important contributions to the development of AI and has written about the need for value alignment in AI systems." .

my:Jordan_Peterson a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Jordan Peterson" ;
my:comment "Psychologist, professor, and author, known for his work on consciousness and the human condition." .

my:Daniel_Dennett a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Daniel Dennett" ;
my:comment "Philosopher and cognitive scientist, known for his work on the philosophy of mind and consciousness." .

my:Sam_Harris a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Sam Harris" ;
my:comment "Neuroscientist and author, known for his work on the nature of consciousness and the intersection of science and spirituality." .

my:Max_Tegmark a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Max Tegmark" ;
my:comment "Physicist and AI researcher, known for his work on the future of AI and the potential risks and benefits of advanced AI." .

my:Lex_Friedman a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Lex Fridman" ;
my:comment "AI researcher and podcaster, known for his work on deep learning and his conversations with experts in AI and related fields." .

my:Alan_Turing a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Alan Turing" ;
my:comment "Father of computer science and AI, developed the Turing Test." .

my:Marvin_Minsky a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Marvin Minsky" ;
my:comment "Pioneer in AI and cognitive science, developed the Society of Mind." .

my:John_McCarthy a my:Influencer ;
my:label "John McCarthy" ;
my:comment "Pioneer in AI and computer science, developed Lisp and time-sharing." .

my:Yann_LeCun a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Yann LeCun" ;
my:comment "Pioneer in deep learning and computer vision, developed convolutional neural networks." .

my:Demis_Hassabis a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Demis Hassabis" ;
my:comment "Co-founder and CEO of DeepMind, pioneer in AI and neuroscience." .

my:Fei_Fei_Li a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Fei-Fei Li" ;
my:comment "Director of the Stanford AI Lab, pioneer in AI and machine learning." .

my:Yoshua_Bengio a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Yoshua Bengio" ;
my:comment "Pioneer in deep learning, co-founder of Mila, and Turing Award winner." .

my:Geoffrey_Hinton a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Geoffrey Hinton" ;
my:comment "Pioneer in deep learning, co-founder of DNNresearch, and Turing Award winner." .

my:Mark_Zuckerberg a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Mark Zuckerberg" ;
my:comment "Co-founder and CEO of Facebook, pioneer in social media and AI-powered technologies." .

my:Elon_Musk a my:Influencer ;
my:label "Elon Musk" ;
my:comment "Entrepreneur and business magnate, pioneer in electric cars, space exploration, and AI-powered technologies." .

